Trinity::

She slowly crept up and hugged onto Aerotaur's neck.  She looked down 
and saw the land far below. She swollowed hard and closed her eyes.  
She started to cringe and held onto his neck a little tigher. 
"How soon untill we get there?" She wanted to get down, but as high 
up as they were, now was not the time to slide off his back.
